nodes.caption: It is important to me to work daily on my HEART POWER!!!! Heart power isn't always #xoxo 😙😙😙😙 and #flowers 💐💐💐💐. It's about the willingness to see the things that are important to the people in my life. It's giving my undivided attention when a friend needs to vent; it's about listening and not trying to give advice that I wouldn't take myself🙄🙄; it's figuring out how I can give support; it's setting my pride aside to be there even when we have disagreements; it's showing up & being present in the moment; saying I'm sorry, saying I didn't have bad intentions; it's talking things out when deep in my bones my body tries to pull away. HEART POWER is knowing that I am not the only person on this planet 🌎  with needs.
